<section class="title-section--where-we-work title-section">
  <div class="center stack">
    <h1>Where we work</h1>
    <p>NRGI works in countries where government actors are open to reform and where accountability actors can inform and support change. Our in-country presence in multiple resource-rich countries enables us to rapidly respond to needs and opportunities.</p>
  </div>
</section>

